data.value: BREAD = Browse Read Edit Add Delete This test will - Read the amount of space in the target - Create the number of directories - Create the Files (Of initial size) - Recurse each file (FindFile/Next) - Increment the size of each file and save - Delete all the above

The Fermenter creates the specified number of files and the specified number of directories.
This will test to make sue the the FileSystems are capable of returning that number from queries. The files should be tidied up after the program exits.
